Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞﾊﾑｰﾄ)グオォーー！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドシュー！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,RAGE OF BAHAMUT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:07.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカン ドカン\Nドカン ドカン…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:09.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:45.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(兵士)退避！\N(兵士)退避！ 船を離れろ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Retreat! Abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:52.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカーン！\N(ﾊﾟﾝ屋)こりゃダメかもな…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:55.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ\Nうちの辺りが爆発したよ 今｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, that explosion was right near our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:57.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ドシュー！\N(一同)ああっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.90,0:01:00.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やべぇ… 逃げろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカーン！\N(一同)ああっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Kaisar...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:12.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)ちょっと あ… あんた➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:14.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しっかりしなさいよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:27.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へ… 陛下…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:31.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ… ぐはっ！ ごほっ ごほっ｡\N(ﾘﾀ)カイザル！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaisar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Death...\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:33.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)し…｡\N(ﾘﾀ)何？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:38.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)真の…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so peaceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:40.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安寧を…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:48.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クゥー クゥ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:52.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅ･ﾄﾞﾗﾝｺﾞ)\Nよかった ヒッポ 無事で｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hippo, I'm so glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ドカーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:06.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(ﾊﾞﾊﾑｰﾄ)グオォーー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to help the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:16.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(父･回想)\N((みんなを助けに行ってくる))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:36.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒッポ… 師匠たちをよろしくね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hippo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of Master and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾌｧﾊﾞﾛ･ﾚｵｰﾈ)ニーナ…｡\Nあっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:58.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,師匠 大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:01.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は大丈夫だ｡ くっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 聞け｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:10.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１０年前\Nバハムートの野郎が現れたとき➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,when Bahamut appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:12.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:18.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守ると約束した女の命を諦めて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I sacrificed the life of a girl\Nthat I promised to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and chose this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:21.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世界を選んだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:26.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は 何を選ぶ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Which will you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get them, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行ってこい ニーナ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about\Nwhat will happen to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:58.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界がどうなろうと そんなもん\Nお前が考える必要なんてねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do us all a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:07.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの野郎に➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:09.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶちかましてやれ～‼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and tear that thing to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:20.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:25.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グオォーー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After the beast is taken down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:46.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾘｵｽ17世)あれを始末して\Nまだ 余が生きていたのなら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I am still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:51.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この命 お前たちの\N好きにしてもらってかまわない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can do as you please with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:58.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾌﾞﾛﾙ)陛下 ご武運を｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,May fortune smile upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:02.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふっ 心にもないことを｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off at the moment\Nwhen His Majesty reaches Dromos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:21.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,陛下が ドロモスに到達したら\Nすぐに離脱しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドシュー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:59.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドォーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:19.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)うっ！ もう もたないよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶﾞﾌﾞﾘｴﾙ)\N全軍 守りに集中するのです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All forces, focus on defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾙｼﾌｪﾙ)持ちこたえるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We will endure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドシュー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:08.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)ニーナ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このときを待っていた｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the moment I've been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:09:01.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ！ なぜ来た!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop!\N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ！\Nやめない！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:08.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが命をささげるなら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to offer up your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then I will too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も一緒にささげる！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to die as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前まで死ぬ必要はない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:30.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は諦めない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not on my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が生きることも\Nあなたが生きることも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And not on yours either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対に諦めない！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:10:00.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞﾊﾑｰﾄ)グオォーー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ビシュー！\Nドシュー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドォーーン‼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:21.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞﾊﾑｰﾄ)グオォーーー‼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アーミラ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Amira...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:04.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,し… 死んだのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:08.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助かった…\N俺たちは助かったんだ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:21.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)\N本当に あの化け物が死んだのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that monster really dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, I'm proud to call you my apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:50.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おめぇは自慢の弟子だぜ ニーナ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:18.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)\N｢お母さん お元気ですか？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still living in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:22.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は今も\N王都での生活を続けています｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(ﾊﾟﾝ屋)ニーナ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持っていきな！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The capital is busy with reconstruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:35.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)｢王都は\N復興の工事で大忙しです｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:39.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そちらは バハムートの被害が\Nあまりなかったと聞いて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so relieved to hear that your area
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,was not badly damaged by Bahamut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とっても ほっとしています｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:47.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)｢あの日\Nいろんなことがありました｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,happened that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:55.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)\N｢きっと私は あの日のことを➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ever be able to forget what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:58.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一生\N忘れることはないと思います｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably never.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)｢たぶん｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The king became a hero that day
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:11.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)｢英雄になった王様は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,at the cost of his sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:14.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの日以来\N目が見えなくなってしまったけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's still the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ 王様をやっています｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(兵士たち)せいっ！\Nせいっ！ せいっ！ せいっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:28.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)そこ～！ 気合いを入れろ！\N(兵士たち)せいっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You there! Put your back into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the humans and the demons\Nhere haven't put the past behind them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)\N｢王都の人と悪魔さんたちは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:34.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 憎しみが消えて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and become great friends or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:37.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲よしというわけには\Nいかないけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:41.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前みたいに\N奴隷とかはなくなったので➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But there aren't slaves like there used to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so their relationship is at least changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:44.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しずつ 関係は\N変化しているのかもしれません｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:49.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌさんは 王都を離れ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that Jeanne left the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and is currently living in the land of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:52.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は\N神の国で生活しているそうです｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bright smiles for all"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When I go home to the village, I plan\Nto go see her on the elder's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:57.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里に帰ったら また\Nおばあちゃんの背中に乗って➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:59.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会いに行くつもりです｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)ありがとう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon, Azazel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:15.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)｢悪魔のアザゼルは…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he went away somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこかへ行ってしまいました｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また来る｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)\N｢バッカスさんは変わらず➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bacchus is his same old self,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:35.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私を家族の一員として\N優しく受け入れてくれています｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,still treating me like family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, young lady! Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)ああ～\Nお嬢さん おクワァえりなさい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:41.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)おっ ニーナ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer are you planning\Non crashing here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:45.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 一体\Nいつまで居座る気だ？ ああっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫ドン(鍋を置く音)\N≫(ﾘﾀ)こら！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:52.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたたちも手伝いなさいよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't any of you helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:57.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)｢リタは あの日\N大切な人を失ってしまったけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rita may have lost someone\Nvery dear to her that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's back on her feet\Nand cooking me delicious meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今では すっかり立ち直り➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:03.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私に おいしいご飯を\N作ってくれています｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:06.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)お嬢さんの声➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The young lady's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It still hasn't returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:10.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり戻りませんねぇ｡\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)ああ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No. To think it would cost her her voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:14.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか 代償が声だとはな…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)おらぁ！\N(２人)うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I told you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:18.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)\N手伝いなさいって言ってるでしょ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ ﾊﾝｻ)は～い｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-Time to eat!\N-Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(一同)いただきます｡\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)いただきま～す！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the offer, but that's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:42.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾄﾞ)ありがたいけど お構いなく｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)これは うまいな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can teach you how to make it if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:51.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)よかったら\N作り方 伝授しましょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you sure?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:54.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)いいのか？\N(ﾘﾀ)ええ｡ 私の代わりに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make it for that drunk\Nand save me the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:57.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの酔っ払いに作ってあげたら？\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)ぶふぅ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:17:01.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾄﾞ)うっ！ ちょっと…｡\Nクゥ～ クゥ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bacchus is in love with Sofiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:03.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)｢バッカスさんは\Nソフィエルさんが好きです｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クワァ～？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Sofiel would never cook for such a fake god!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾄﾞ)\Nソフィエル様が こんなエセ神に➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:11.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,料理など作るか！\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)誰がエセ神だ バカ野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a fake god, you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:13.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パチパチ パチパチ\N(ﾊﾝｻ)クワァ～ クゥ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you guys cut it out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:15.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)\Nおめぇらも はしゃぐんじゃねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:17.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)クワァ～ クワッ クワッ｡\Nふふっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:20.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)\Nお… おめぇ 笑ってんじゃねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this isn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to introduce\Nthese wonderful people to you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:23.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)\N｢いつか このすてきな人たちを➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:25.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さんに紹介しますね｣｡\N(ﾘﾄﾞ)今 なんと言った？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-What did you just say?\N-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:29.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)だから ｢バカ野郎｣…｡\N≪随分 盛り上がってるじゃねぇか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like y'all are having fun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:35.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あら｡ あんたの分の料理は\N作ってないわよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I would have made more food\Nif I knew you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:37.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつは残念だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't come by to eat today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:40.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど 今日は\N飯を食いに来たわけじゃねぇんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd get going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ行こうと思ってな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:55.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)そうか｡\Nおう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-I see.\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never liked the capital much anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:59.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もともと 俺は\Nこの王都って場所が苦手でよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time I get back to my life of wandering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:02.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,放浪生活に戻ろうってな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つぅわけで 明日の朝には出る｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, I'll be departing tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:19.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,元気でな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:32.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ？ どうした？\Nハグでもしてほしいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? You want a hug or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:45.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢あのとき 会った｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"I met her then."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:47.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？ 誰に？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Met who?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:55.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢バハムートの光の中で｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Inside Bahamut's light..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"I met a woman."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢女の人に｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,SHE WISHES...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU THE BEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:36.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとな ニーナ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, which way does the wind blow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナ 風は どっちに吹いてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Since coming to the capital,\Nthere have been happy times,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:20:02.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)｢王都に来てから\Nうれしいこと 楽しいこと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,fun times
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and sad times where I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:05.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悲しくて泣いてしまうこと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So much has happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:09.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いろんなことが\Nいっぱいあったけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but, Mom, I'm still doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:13.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さん\N私は これからも元気です！｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:37.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:44.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴゴゴゴッ…\Nドドォーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bahamut isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:10.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バハムートは死んじゃいねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:12.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだろ？ アーミラ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Amira?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:19.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙの声)ファバロ～！\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Favaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:30.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあっ！\Nヒヒィーン！(馬のいななき)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.42,0:23:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see him again soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:41.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また すぐに会えるわよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.99,0:24:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,BAHASOUL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Baha Baha Baha Soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.78,0:24:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for watching!
